text: Onesidezero is the second studio album by Onesidezero, released on June 5, 2007. This album was released almost six years after their major label debut Is This Room Getting Smaller. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== Onesidezero: * Jasan Radford — vocals * Levon Sultanian — guitars, backing vocals * Cristian Hernandez — bass, backing vocals * Rob Basile — drums ==References== * Category:2007 albums Category:Onesidezero albums Category:Corporate Punishment Records albums Category:Albums produced by Ulrich Wild
